inuing%20to%20rock%20the%20central%20Myanmar%20city%20of%20more%20than%201.7%20million%20people%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sticky%20heat%20has%20exhausted%20rescue%20workers%20and%20accelerated%20body%20decomposition%2C%20which%20could%20complicate%20identification%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20desperate%20scene%20unfolded%20at%20a%20collapsed%20apartment%20block%20in%20Myanmar's%20second%20biggest%20city%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20when%20rescuers%20thought%20they%20had%20saved%20the%20life%20of%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20trapped%20under%20the%20rubble%20for%20more%20than%2055%20hours.%20They%20amputated%20her%20leg%20to%20free%20her%2C%20but%20after%20pulling%20her%20out%2C%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20everything%20to%20save%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20medical%20responders%20told%20AFP%2C%20but%20she%20had%20lost%20too%20much%20blood%20from%20the%20amputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20worshipers%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20gathered%20near%20a%20destroyed%20mosque%20in%20the%20city%20on%20Monday%20morning%20for%20the%20first%20prayer%20of%20Eid%20al-Fitr%2C%20the%20holiday%20that%20follows%20the%20Islamic%20fasting%20month%20of%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunerals%20for%20hundreds%20of%20victims%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%207.7-magnitude%20quake%20struck%20near%20Mandalay%20early%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20followed%20minutes%20later%20by%20a%206.7-magnitude%20aftershock.%20The%20tremors%20collapsed%20buildings%2C%20downed%20bridges%20and%20buckled%20roads%2C%20with%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20destruction%20seen%20in%20central%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Federation%20of%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Societies%20launched%20an%20emergency%20appeal%20Sunday%20for%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20to%20help%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20largest%20humanitarian%20network%20said%20needs%20were%20growing%20by%20the%20hour%20as%20rising%20temperatures%20and%20the%20approaching%20monsoon%20season%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20%26quot%3Bsecondary%20crises%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20facing%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20country%20of%20over%2050%20million%20people%20were%20immense%20even%20before%20the%20earthquake.%20Myanmar%20has%20been%20ravaged%20by%20four%20years%20of%20civil%20war%20sparked%20by%20a%20military%20coup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20have%20emerged%20of%20sporadic%20fighting%20even%20after%20the%20quake%2C%20with%20one%20rebel%20group%20telling%20AFP%20on%20Sunday%20that%20seven%20of%20its%20fighters%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20aerial%20attack%20soon%20after%20the%20tremors%20hit.%20Before%20Friday's%20quake%2C%20some%203.5%20million%20people%20were%20displaced%20by%20the%20raging%20civil%20war%2C%20many%20at%20risk%20of%20hunger.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743394980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fhkmls91_myanmar-earthquake_625x300_31_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeadly-myanmar-earthquake-unleashed-energy-of-334-atomic-bombs-report-8051164%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20powerful%207.7-magnitude%20earthquake%2C%20which%20killed%20around%201700%20people%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20has%20unleashed%20energy%20equivalent%20to%20over%20300%20atomic%20bombs%20combined%2C%20according%20to%20a%20leading%20American%20geologist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdeadly-myanmar-earthquake-unleashed-energy-of-334-atomic-bombs-report-8051164%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Will%20chop%2C%20pack%20you%20in%20drum%20like%20Meerut%20massacre'%3A%20UP%20woman%20threatens%20to%20kill%20husband%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743394353000%2C