uake%20that%20struck%20central%20Myanmar.%20The%20unfinished%20building%20crumbled%20in%20seconds%2C%20sending%20a%20cloud%20of%20dust%20and%20debris%20into%20the%20air%20and%20trapping%20dozens%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20Major%20General%20Nopasin%20Poolswat%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20Bureau%2C%20said%20that%20four%20Chinese%20nationals%20were%20apprehended%20for%20illegally%20removing%2032%20files%20of%20documents%20from%20the%20rear%20of%20the%20collapsed%20State%20Audit%20Office%20(SAO)%20building%2C%20without%20permission%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Thailand.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmyanmar-earthquake-thailand-earthquake-a-china-connection-in-bangkoks-33-storey-building-brought-down-by-quake-8045516%5C%22%3EChina%20Connection%20Emerges%20In%20Bangkok%20Skyscraper%20That%20Collapsed%20During%20Quake%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20powerful%20quake%2C%20the%20Bangkok%20Governor%20declared%20the%20area%20of%20the%20building%20collapse%20a%20disaster%20zone%2C%20thereby%20designating%20it%20as%20a%20restricted%20area%20where%20no%20one%20was%20allowed%20to%20enter%20without%20authorization.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20said%20that%20on%20Saturday%2C%20they%20received%20information%20about%20some%20individuals%20removing%20documents%20from%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20investigation%2C%20they%20located%20one%20of%20the%20Chinese%20men%20near%20the%20incident%20site%2C%20who%20claimed%20he%20was%20the%20project%20manager%20for%20a%20building%20construction%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20probe%2C%20it%20was%20confirmed%20that%20the%20apprehended%20man%20had%20a%20valid%20work%20permit%20and%20that%20his%20company%20was%20employed%20by%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Italian-Thai%20Development%20Public%20Company%20Limited%2C%20the