one%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20parents'%20immigration%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20legal%20scholars%20have%20largely%20dismissed%20this%20as%20unconstitutional%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20get%20it%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20leaving%20open%20the%20possibility%20of%20pursuing%20executive%20actions%20or%20constitutional%20amendments.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20maybe%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20people.%20But%20we%20have%20to%20end%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20He%20inaccurately%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20the%20only%20country%20that%20has%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%2034%20other%20nations%20also%20offering%20unrestricted%20birthright%20citizenship%2C%20reported%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743390780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0964mmj4_dallas-march_625x300_31_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthousands-march-in-dallas-to-protest-trumps-immigration-policies-8050844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20massive%20crowd%20marched%20through%20downtown%20Dallas%20today%2C%20protesting%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20immigration%20policies%20and%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20students%20who%20have%20been%20detained%20by%20immigration%20officials%20across%20the%20country%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20CNN.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthousands-march-in-dallas-to-protest-trumps-immigration-policies-8050844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20York%20Doctor's%20%26quot%3BLong%20Live%20Hamas%26quot%3B%20Social%20Media%20Post%20Lands%20Her%20In%20Trouble%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20City%20doctor%20has%20been%20fired%20after%20posting%20%26quot%3BLong%20Live%20Hamas%20%26amp%3B%20Hezbollah%26quot%3B%20online%20and%20making%20statements%20denying%C2%A0atrocities%20by%20the%20militant%20groups.%20Lila%20Abassi%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20Mount%20Sinai's%20Upper%20East%20Side%20hospital%2C%20was%20let%20go%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20a%20probe%20into%20her%20controversial%20social%20media%20activity%2C%20a%20hospital%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F03%2F29%2Fus-news%2Fmount-sinai-doctor-fired-for-posts-denying-october-7-attacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20NY%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20a%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20that%20controls%20Gaza%2C%20while%20Hezbollah%20is%20an%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%20based%20in%20Lebanon.%20Both%20are%20labelled%20terrorist%20organisations%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Israel%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20posts%2C%20Ms%20Abassi%2C%2046%2C%20allegedly%20praised%20Hamas%20as%20%26quot%3Bnoble%20resistance%20and%20freedom%20fighters%2C%26quot%3B%20called%20the%20Israeli%20army%20a%20%26quot%3Bplague%2C%26quot%3B%20accused%20Israel%20of%20%26quot%3Bslaughtering%20babies%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20dismissed%20reports%20of%20sexual%20violence%20during%20the%20October%207%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20show%20me%20actual%20rape%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20a%20Facebook%20doctors'%20group%2C%20using%20the%20pseudonym%20%26quot%3BKluver%20Bucy%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20a%20rare%20neurological%20disorder.%20She%20also%20claimed%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bmassacr%5Bed%5D%20more%20people%20on%2010%2F7%20than%20%5Bwere%5D%20killed%20by%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbassi%20is%20a%202011%20graduate%20of%20St.%20George's%20University%20School%20of%20Medicine%20who%20later%20completed%20her%20residency%20at%20SUNY%20Downstate.%20Her%20firing%20came%20after%20weeks%20of%20pressure%20from%20New%20York%20City%20Councilwoman%20Inna%20