20Sunday%20slammed%20attempts%20to%20incite%20communal%20tension%20over%20Aurangazeb's%20tomb%20and%20said%20history%20shouldn't%20be%20viewed%20from%20the%20prism%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20Thackeray%20also%20asked%20people%20not%20to%20rely%20on%20WhatsApp%20forwards%20for%20historical%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20his%20annual%20Gudhi%20Padwa%20rally%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%20here%2C%20Raj%C2%A0Thackeray%20said%20the%20Mughal%20ruler%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bkill%20a%20thought%20called%20Shivaji%26quot%3B%20but%20failed%20and%20died%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfzal%20Khan%2C%20the%20Bijapur%20general%2C%20was%20buried%20near%20the%20Pratapgadh%20Fort%20and%20it%20couldn't%20have%20been%20done%20without%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj's%20permission%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%C2%A0Thackeray's%20comments%20came%20amid%20demands%20by%20right-wing%20outfits%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20Aurangzeb's%20tomb%20located%20in%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20district.%20Protests%20over%20the%20issue%20had%20also%20triggered%20violence%20in%20Nagpur%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20we%20want%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20these%20people%20sought%20to%20destroy%20the%20Marathas%20but%20were%20wiped%20out%20instead.%20Stop%20reading%20history%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20rather%20delve%20into%20history%20books%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20people%20not%20to%20get%20provoked%20and%20distracted%2C%20he%20said%20that%20socio-political%20situations%20were%20different%20in%20pre-Shivaji%20and%20post-Shivaji%20eras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20forgotten%20the%20real%20issues%20of%20the%20present%20time.%20Hindus%20who%20feel%20awakened%20after%20a%20movie%20are%20of%20no%20use.%20Did%20you%20learn%20about%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj's%20sacrifice%20because%20of%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20and%20about%20Aurangazeb%20because%20of%20Akshaye%20Khanna%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20recently%20released%20period%20drama%20'Chhaava'%2C%20based%20on%20the%20life%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%2C%20who%20was%20tortured%20and%20executed%20by%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Aurangzeb%20was%20born%20in%20Dahod%2C%20Gujarat.%20Those%20who%20provoke%20people%20for%20their%20selfish%20political%20aspirations%20are%20not%20concerned%20with%20history%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%C2%A0Thackeray%20said%20a%20country%20cannot%20progress%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20and%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Turkey%20and%20how%20it%20%26quot%3Breformed%26quot%3B%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReligion%20should%20remain%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20your%20home.%20A%20Hindu%20identifies%20as%20a%20Hindu%20only%20when%20Muslims%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20or%20during%20riots%3B%20otherwise%2C%20Hindus%20are%20divided%20by%20caste%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MNS%20chief%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20government's%20popular%20'Mukhyamantri%20Majhi%20Ladki%20Bahin'%20scheme%20would%20be%20scrapped.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20you%20earlier%2C%20but%20you%20believed%20them%20and%20not%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20been%20attacking%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20in%20the%20state%20for%20not%20raising%20the%20monthly%20financial%20assistance%20under%20the%20Ladki%20Bahin%20programme%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%202%2C100%20as%20promised%20in%20their%20poll%20manifesto%20before%20last%20year's%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%C2%A0Thackeray%20reiterated%20his%20party's%20stand%20on%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Marathi%20language%20being%20made%20mandatory%20for%20official%20purposes.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20live%20here%20and%20don't%20speak%20the%20language%2C%20you%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20appropriatel