leged%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20impotent%20and%20refused%20to%20cohabit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20said%20if%20the%20petitioner%20wants%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20allegations%20of%20impotency%20are%20baseless%2C%20he%20can%20undergo%20the%20concerned%20medical%20test%20or%20produce%20any%20other%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20cannot%20possibly%20be%20permitted%20to%20subject%20the%20wife%20to%20undergo%20her%20virginity%20test%20and%20fill%20up%20the%20lacuna%20in%20his%20evidence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20passed%20on%20January%209%20was%20made%20available%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20contention%20of%20the%20petitioner%20demanding%20a%20virginity%20test%20of%20his%20wife%20is%20unconstitutional%20as%20it%20violates%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20which%20includes%20the%20right%20to%20dignity%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArticle%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20not%20only%20guarantees%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty%20but%20also%20the%20right%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20woman%20can%20be%20forced%20to%20conduct%20her%20virginity%20test.%20It%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20fundamental%20rights%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20borne%20in%20mind%20that%20Article%2021%20is%20the%20'heart%20of%20fundamental%20rights'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Verma%20further%20said%20that%20the%20virginity%20test%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20basic%20right%20of%20women%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20decency%20and%20proper%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20personal%20liberty%20enshrined%20under%20Article%2021%20is%20non-derogable%20and%20cannot%20be%20tinkered%20with%20in%20any%20manner.%20The%20petitioner%20cannot%20possibly%20be%20permitted%20to%20subject%20the%20wife%20to%20undergo%20her%20virginity%20test%20and%20fill%20up%20the%20lacuna%20in%20his%20evidence%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20but%20in%20any%20case%2C%20granting%20the%20permission%20for%20virginity%20test%20of%20the%20respondent%20would%20be%20against%20her%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20the%20cardinal%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%20and%20secret%20modesty%20of%20a%20female%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-derogable%20human%20rights%20refer%20to%20rights%20that%20are%20absolute%20and%20may%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20any%20derogation%2C%20even%20in%20times%20of%20war%20or%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20further%20observed%20that%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20both%20parties%20against%20each%20other%20are%20the%20subject%20matter%20of%20evidence%20and%20a%20conclusion%20can%20be%20drawn%20only%20after%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Court%20is%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20the%20order%20impugned%20is%20neither%20illegal%20nor%20perverse%20and%20there%20is%20no%20judicial%20error%20committed%20by%20the%20trial%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20got%20married%20on%20April%2030%2C%202023%2C%20as%20per%20Hindu%20rites.%20They%20lived%20together%20at%20the%20husband's%20family%20residence%20in%20Korba%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wife%20allegedly%20told%20her%20family%20members%20that%20her%20husband%20is%20impotent%20and%20she%20refused%20to%20establish%20a%20marital%20relationship%20or%20cohabit%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20the%20petitioner's%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20filed%20an%20interim%20application%20on%20July%202%2C%202024%2C%20under%20section%20144%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagrik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20(BNSS)%20before%20the%20family%20court%20in%20Raigarh%20district%20seeking%20maintenance%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20from%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20maintenance%20claim%20interim%20application%2C%20the%20petitioner%20sought%20a%20virginity%20test%20of%20his%20wife%20alleging%20that%20she%20was%20in%20an%20illicit%20relationship%20with%20her%20brother-in-law.%20He%20claimed%20the%20marriage%20was%20never%20consummated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2015%2C%202024%2C%20the%20family%20court%20in%20Raigarh%20rejected%20the%20husband's%20request%20following%20which%20he%20filed%20a%20criminal%20petition%20in%20the%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20currently%20at%20evidence%20stage%20in%20the%20family%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743355980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frvhchll_chhattisgarh-high-court_625x300_18_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-cant-be-forced-to-take-virginity-test-violates-right-to-dignity-chhattisgarh-high-court-8048917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chhattisgarh%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20a%20woman%20cannot%20be%20forced%20to%20undergo%20a%20virginity%20test%20which%20violates%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20that%20guarantees%20her%20fundamental%20right%20to%20protection%20of%20life%20and%20liberty%2C%20including%20the%20right%20to%20dignity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-cant-be-forced-to-take-virginity-test-violates-right-to-dignity-chhattisgarh-high-court-8048917%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22500-Year-Old%20Telugu%20Rock%20Inscription%20Found%20In%20Telangana's%20Anantgiri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETelugu%20inscriptions%20dating%20back%20to%201517%20CE%20have%20been%20found%20in%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India.%20%C2%A0The%20find%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20inscriptions%20and%20rock%20art%20was%20found%20in%20neighbouring%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20team%20found%20the%20inscriptions%20at%20Narasimhulagutta%2C%20Anantagiri%2C%20Rajanna%20Sircilla%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20inscription%20is%20a%20praise%20of%20various%20local%20Hindu%20gods%2C%20and%20records%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Vishnu%20temple%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill%20in%20Anantagiri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20inscriptions%20that%20are%20800%20to%202000%20years%20old%20were%20found%20in%20Lankkamala%20Reserve%20Forest%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20survey%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20also%20found%20rock%20art%20thought%20to%20be%20from%20the%20megalithic%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20said%20to%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeep-in-andhra-forest-treasure-trove-of-rock-paintings-inscriptions-7840448%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20archaeological%20find%20in%20recent%20times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20led%20to%20the%20discovery%20of%20three%20rock%20shelters.%20One%20of%20these%20contained%20stunning%20prehistoric%20paintings%20depicting%20animals%2C%20geometric%20patterns%2C%20and%20human%20figures%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paintings%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Megalithic%20(Iron%20Age)%20and%20early%20historic%20periods%20(2500%20BCE-2nd%20century%20CE)%2C%20were%20created%20using%20natural%20materials%20like%20red%20ochre%2C%20kaolin%2C%20animal%20fat%2C%20and%20crushed%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20also%20has%20a%20rich%20heritage%20in%20terms%20of%20rock%20inscriptions%20that%20provide%20glimpses%20of%20its%20history.%20Last%20year%2C%20an%20ASI%20team%20found%20three%20inscriptions%20from%20the%20Chalukya%20period%20in